<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="features-and-workflow">Features and Workflow</h3>
<p>What’s most exciting is that I added a small <code>JavaScript</code> snippet to enable a “view code” feature for images (though in principle, it’s simply toggling a collapsed code block). Click the <code>&lt;/&gt;</code> icon in the top‑right corner of an image to expand the corresponding <code>Mathematica</code> or <code>TikZ</code> code—like this:</p>
